column2: select u.*, &&& + cast(p.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(p.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as url, ltrim(str(p.ra,#,#)) as ra, ltrim(str(p.dec,#,#)) as dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type from #x x, #upload u, photoTag p  where u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID=p.objID and p.mode=# order by x.up_id
